When one wants to add API:

1) look for the specs on developers.google.com 
    
    https://developers.google.com/admin-sdk/directory/v1/reference/users)

2) look for the js wrapper in github

    https://github.com/googleapis/google-api-nodejs-client/blob/master/src/apis/admin/directory_v1.ts

    https://github.com/googleapis/google-api-nodejs-client/blob/master/src/apis/calendar/v3.ts

3) enable from google cloud console the api

    https://console.developers.google.com/apis/dashboard

4) assign the clientID the scope needed
    
    https://admin.google.com/aegee.eu/AdminHome?chromeless=1#OGX:ManageOauthClients
